  2→//!
  3→//! Authentication uses the GitHub device-flow OAuth to obtain a GitHub token,
  4→//! then exchanges it for a short-lived Copilot API token via
  5→//! `https://api.github.com/copilot_internal/v2/token`.
  6→//!
  7→//! The Copilot API itself is OpenAI-compatible (`/chat/completions`).
